<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="roast-v">roast <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rəʊst/    美 /roʊst/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>烤；烘：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Food will include buffalo that will be roasted over an open fire.  
食物将包括在明火上烧烤的美洲野牛肉。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The meat is roasting in the oven. 
肉正在炉子里烤着。</p></div></div>